OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779379877
OL,3,CDangerous driver jailed after killing
OL,4,Cmotorcyclist
OL,6,FA dangerous driver has been jailed
OL,7,Fafter killing a motorcyclist in
OL,8,FSittingbourne.
OL,10,FCollette Gibson was travelling
OL,11,Fnorthwards on the A249 Maidstone Road
OL,12,Ftowards the Key Street roundabout at
OL,13,F3.20pm on Saturday 23rd April 2022,
OL,14,Fwhen she suddenly stopped without any
OL,15,Fwarning or reason.
OL,17,FA car following her Vauxhall Zafira
OL,18,Fcollided with her vehicle and a
OL,19,Fmotorcyclist riding behind both
OL,20,Fcollided with the rear car.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
