FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779379877
OL,3,CDangerous driver jailed after killing
OL,4,Cmotorcyclist
OL,6,FThe rider, a man in his 50s, died at
OL,7,Fthe scene.
OL,9,FDetectives launched an investigation
OL,10,Fand witnesses stated they saw no
OL,11,Freason for Gibson to slow or stop.
OL,13,FThe 55 year old was subsequently
OL,14,Fcharged with causing death by
OL,15,Fdangerous driving.
OL,17,FShe denied the charge at Maidstone
OL,18,FCrown Court but was found guilty by a
OL,19,Fjury at the same court on Wednesday 25
OL,20,FMarch.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
