FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779379877
OL,3,CDangerous driver jailed after killing
OL,4,Cmotorcyclist
OL,6,FGibson, of South Ockendon, Essex, was
OL,7,Fsentenced to five years in prison on
OL,8,FWednesday 20 May 2026.
OL,10,FShe was also disqualified from driving
OL,11,Ffor four and a half years and will
OL,12,Fhave to complete an extended re-test.
OL,14,FDetective Constable Sara Capozzi said:
OL,15,F"Gibson's actions resulted in a man's
OL,16,Fdeath through no fault of his own.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
