PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779379877
OL,3,CDangerous driver jailed after killing
OL,4,Cmotorcyclist
OL,6,F"She has consistently denied the
OL,7,Fcharge as well as refuting the
OL,8,Ftestimony of numerous witnesses,
OL,9,Fmaking her victim's family relive this
OL,10,Ftragic incident in court.
OL,12,F"We are satisfied Gibson will now face
OL,13,Fthe consequence of her actions and we
OL,14,Fhope this brings some closure to the
OL,15,Fman's loved ones."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
